'''Killscent''' was a secretion produced by [[slashrat]]s when they sensed they had mortally wounded their prey. It was a combination of sweat and pheromones that could be sensed by air and underground, as it soaked into the soil. Killscent attracted other slashrats from miles around, surrounding the prey in a savage feeding frenzy called a [[killball]].

[[Agamar/Legends|Agamari]] scientists Dr. [[Anki Pace]] and [[Jens (student)|Jens]] became familiar enough with the biology of [[slashrat]]s that they developed a synthetic form of killscent that could be used to attract slashrats to a target or distract them for several minutes.

